Input file for pb calculation for protein petide system for MD-sim. with Charmm FF


&general
sys_name="Prot-Pept",
startframe=1,
temperature=310
PBRadii=7 # needed to apply as charmm ff is used and restricts us to pb
/
&pb
indi=5, # value chosen from https://www.frontiersin.org/journals/chemistry/articles/10.3389/fchem.2020.573259/full
exdi=80 # actually 80 is alr. the standard value
/
